sp23_barcrawl.eventDetails: Join ACM and meet your fellow members as we visit, KAMS, Joe's, and Legends on our semesterly bar crawl! Get a free t-shirt with sign-up! Alcohol will be provided by ACM to members over 21 wearing bar crawl t-shirts.  We will also be hosting an official pregame (details released closer to the event)! This ticket does not pay for cover at the bars.
